# Runtime dependency intent for the NeuroMultiverse analysis package.
# Edit this file, then regenerate requirements-lock.txt with the resolver
# command recorded in docs/reproducibility.md. Do not hand-edit the lock file.
#
# GPU-enabled PyTorch is deliberately absent here: its wheel index depends on
# the local NVIDIA driver and is resolved separately into
# requirements-gpu-lock.txt.

-e .
